INSTALL SCRIPT AND CONFIGURATION
---------------------------------
cp -av switch-wifi.sh /usr/bin/
cp switch-wifi.conf /etc/

CRON JOB SETUP
--------------
$crontab -e
add below entry
* * * * * /usr/bin/switch-wifi.sh >> /var/tmp/switch-wifi.log


LOGROTATE SETUP
---------------
/etc/logrotate.d/switch-wifi
/var/tmp/switch-wifi.log {
  maxsize 10K
  rotate 5
  su root root
  monthly
  compress
  missingok
  notifempty
}
